				<wikidot:authorName>MaliceAforethought</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2902864</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Loved this as a draft, and I love it here. It's wild and emotional in just the right amounts, in just the right ways, and the anomaly is brilliantly effective and vivid. The dual emotional and physical explosions were a very nice touch, and it all adds up to an article that I'm genuinely impressed you managed to pull off in two days.</p> 
				 	]]>
